title: LoL Match History website not loading.
body:
Been like this for the last 2 days. LoL status page reads all is good, is there something I'm missing?

http://imgur.com/1AQapFp

replies.body: I looked up your match history, [linked here](http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA1/209950273), without any issue.  You may need to clear your cache or try another browser to see if it works.  I hope that helps!
